high_descs: Turn around ad walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the butter knife off of the white table.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door and put the butter knife in the cup inside.
Take the cup with the butter knife in it out of the cabinet and close the door.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the cup with the butter knife in it on the front edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the near end of the table with the green sponge.
Pick up the knife that is behind the sponge.
Turn around and go to the cabinet above the brown paper bag.
Put the knife in the goblet that is on the lower cabinet shelf.
Pick up the goblet with the knife in it.
Lower the goblet to counter height.
Put the goblet near the front edge of the counter, in front of the jar of utensils.
anns.task_desc: Place a goblet holding a knife on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the rectangular white table near the window
Pick p the butter knife from the table
Turn around and walk up to the kitchen counter right of the sink
Open the cabinet above the paper bag on the counter
Put the knife in the wine glass in the cabinet then pick up the wine glass
Look down to face the counter right of the sink
Put the wine glass on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the wine glass with knife on the kitchen counter
